    <abstract>
      <t>   This document specifies a mechanism to facilitate widespread
   multicast connectivity over the Global Internet via dynamic
   tunneling, enabling many different multicast islands to be connected
   by tunnels between both PIM routers and AMT gateways/relays.

	 </t>
